    <item>
      <title>Padrino 0.14.2 release</title>
      <link>http://padrinorb.com/blog/padrino-0-14-2/</link>
      <description>&lt;h2 id="changes"&gt;Changes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX router in non-Padrino applications (&lt;a href="https://github.com/adam12"&gt;@adam12&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/commit/04f64706613f08f4f5eaddd18afec8ce4d1855d9" title="#2154"&gt;#2154&lt;/a&gt; padrino-admin haml layout (&lt;a href="https://github.com/ujifgc" title="ujifgc"&gt;ujifgc&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX Datamapper tasks (&lt;a href="https://github.com/adam12"&gt;@adam12&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/1979" title="#1979"&gt;#1979&lt;/a&gt; Add a Default Rake Task If Test Framework is Included (&lt;a href="https://github.com/ujifgc" title="ujifgc"&gt;ujifgc&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2150" title="#2150"&gt;#2150&lt;/a&gt; Project generator silently ignores invalid -a option (&lt;a href="https://github.com/ujifgc" title="ujifgc"&gt;ujifgc&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2152" title="#2152"&gt;#2152&lt;/a&gt; using open without requiring &lt;code&gt;open-uri&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href="https://github.com/ujifgc" title="ujifgc"&gt;ujifgc&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FIX &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2163" title="#2163"&gt;#2163&lt;/a&gt; preserve spaces in args of padrino gen (&lt;a href="https://github.com/ujifgc" title="ujifgc"&gt;ujifgc&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NEW &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/pull/2161" title="#2161"&gt;#2161&lt;/a&gt; allow array as tag attribute (&lt;a href="https://github.com/aeris" title="aeris"&gt;aeris&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Sequel usage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update &lt;a href="https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/commit/f45566335f0b676d9dc2a8e7de68babc2274ff44" title="ActiveRecord::Migration usage"&gt;ActiveRecord::Migration usage&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href="https://github.com/adam12"&gt;@adam12&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
      <pubDate>Tue, 8 May 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://padrinorb.com/blog/padrino-0-14-2/</guid>
    </item>
